### 2. 查詢 test_dynamic.products 中的所有商品
POST http://localhost:8080/api/postgres/db/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}"
}

### 3. 依據 SKU 查詢特定商品
POST http://localhost:8080/api/postgres/db/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}",
  "sku": "SKU-001"
}

### 4. 依據產品名稱模糊查詢
POST http://localhost:8080/api/postgres/db/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}",
  "productName": "iPhone"
}

### 5. 依據類別查詢
POST http://localhost:8080/api/postgres/db/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}",
  "categoryId": 200
}

### 6. 依據價格範圍查詢
POST http://localhost:8080/api/postgres/db/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}",
  "minListPrice": 20000.00,
  "maxListPrice": 50000.00
}

### 7. 只查詢有效商品（is_active = true）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/postgres/db/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}",
  "isActive": true,
  "limit": 5
}

### 8. 複合查詢（類別 + 價格範圍 + 有效狀態）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/postgres/db/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}",
  "categoryId": 200,
  "minListPrice": 25000.00,
  "maxListPrice": 45000.00,
  "isActive": true
}

### 9. 關閉資料庫連線
POST http://localhost:8080/api/db/close
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "connectionId": "{{connectionId}}"
}